member.name: T:SwedishNationalId.NationalId
member.summary: Represents Swedish Personal Identification Number and Organization Number. Handles the following formats: YYMMDD-CCCC YYMMDDCCCC, YYYYMMDD-CCCC and YYYYMMDDCCCC ///

member.name: T:SwedishNationalId.Ssn
member.summary: Immutable class that represents swedish personal identificatio number. Understands formats YYMMDD-CCCC, YYMMDDCCCC, YYYYMMDD-CCCC and YYYYMMDDCCCC. Uses format YYYYMMDDCCCC when converting to string.

member.name: T:SwedishNationalId.OrganisationNumber
member.summary: Immutable class that represents swedish organisation number. Understands formats YYMMDD-CCCC and YYMMDDCCCC. Uses format YYMMDDCCCC when converting to string.
